scripts.preinstall:
node -e "!process.env.npm_config_user_agent.startsWith('pnpm/') && !process.argv.filter(x=>x=='--force').length && !console.warn('

Recommended to use \`npx pnpm install\` or \`pnpm install\` to install dependencies in this repository.
Use \`npm install --force\` to install with npm.

') && process.exit(-1)"
